## Contributor model
| Property | Definition | Value type | Repeatable |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| name | Names associated with a contributor. Contributor name types must be from the "contributor.name" controlled list and multipart name types must be from the "contributor.name.structuredValue" controlled list. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| type | Entity type of the contributor (person, organization, etc.). Contributor types must be from the "contributor" controlled list. | String | No |
| status | Status of the contributor relative to other parallel contributors (e.g. the primary author among a group of contributors). Use "primary" to indicate preferred status. | String | No |
| role | Relationships of the contributor to the resource or to an event in its history. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| identifier | Identifiers and URIs associated with the contributor entity. Contributor identifier types must be from the "contributor.identifier" controlled list. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| affiliation | Institutional or other affiliation associated with a contributor. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| note | Other information associated with the contributor. Contributor note types must be from the "contributor.note" controlled list. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| valueAt | URL or other pointer to the location of the contributor information. | String | No |

## Event model
| Property | Definition | Value type | Repeatable |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| type | Description of the event (creation, publication, etc.). Event types must be from the "event" controlled list. | String | No |
| displayLabel | The preferred display label to use for the event in access systems. | String | No |
| date | Dates associated with the event. See event date types, multipart date types, and date note types. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| contributor | Contributors associated with the event. See all contributor types. | Object (Contributor model) | Yes |
| location | Locations associated with the event. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| identifier | Identifiers and URIs associated with the event. Identifier types must be from the "identifier" controlled list. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| note | Other information about the event. Event note types must be from the "event.note" controlled list. | Object (Description model) | Yes |
| valueLanguage | Language of the descriptive metadata value. | Object (Value language model) | No |
| structuredValue | Imprint statement given as place, publisher, date, and/or any other relevant information. | Object (Description model) | Yes |

